2005-12-07

Stereo Test Kit records

The excellent Stereo Test Kit records are doing a buy two get one free offer at their web store so you can fill your boots with dreamy, melancholic Swedish pop.

The very excellent EP by Audrey is almost certainly a late arrival in my end of year list and the just as lovely we are soldiers we have guns are probably going to be thereabouts as well.

  • we are soldires we have guns - Damn those TV shows...(mp3)
